            <fr:title text="Quaternion Group">Quaternion Group</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>example</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">Dummit and Foote <fr:link href="/dummit-2004-abstract/" title="Abstract Algebra" uri="http://localhost:8000/dummit-2004-abstract/" display-uri="dummit-2004-abstract" type="local">Abstract Algebra</fr:link> Section 1.5</fr:meta>
            <fr:meta name="source">Hungerford <fr:link href="/hungerford-1974-algebra/" title="Algebra" uri="http://localhost:8000/hungerford-1974-algebra/" display-uri="hungerford-1974-algebra" type="local">Algebra</fr:link> Exercise 1.2.3</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>We may define the <html:dfn>Quaternion Group</html:dfn> as consisting of the set <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Q_{8}=\{-1\}\cup \{i^{m}j^{n}k^{p}\mid  0\leq  m,n,p\leq  3\}]]></fr:tex> where we identify <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[1=i^{0}j^{0}k^{0}]]></fr:tex> and it obeys the identities
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[i^{2}=j^{2}=k^{2}=ijk=-1]]></fr:tex>
and so we write <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[-i=i^{3}]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[-j=j^{3}]]></fr:tex>, and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[-k=k^{3}]]></fr:tex>, and also
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[(-1)^{2}=1.]]></fr:tex>
We have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(-1)i=-i]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(-1)j=-j]]></fr:tex>, and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(-1)k=-k]]></fr:tex>.
After a bit of work, we find
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ij=-ji=k]]></fr:tex>
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[jk=-kj=i]]></fr:tex>
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ki=-ik=j]]></fr:tex></html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="/alex-nelson/" title="Alex Nelson" uri="http://localhost:8000/alex-nelson/" display-uri="alex-nelson" type="local">Alex Nelson</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>13</fr:day>
